question: Display day spas and wellness retreats that cost 150.0.
sql_query1:
SELECT Relaxation_spot.Name 
FROM Relaxation_spot
WHERE (Relaxation_spot.type = "Day Spa" OR Relaxation_spot.type = "Wellness Retreat") AND Relaxation_spot.price = 150.0
sql_query2:
SELECT Relaxation_spot.Name 
FROM Relaxation_spot
WHERE Relaxation_spot.type = "Day Spa" OR Relaxation_spot.type = "Wellness Retreat" AND Relaxation_spot.price = 150.0
interpretation1: Which day spas cost 150.0 and which wellness retreats cost the same amount?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all day spas and also provide a list of wellness retreats that cost 150.0.
